<para style="q1">

<verse number="39" style="v" />He called to mind that they were made of flesh,</para>

<para style="q1">a wind that passes away and does not return.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="40" style="v" />How often they rebelled against him in the wilderness</para>

<para style="q1">and grieved him in the barren regions!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="41" style="v" />Again and again they challenged God</para>

<para style="q1">and offended the Holy One of Israel.</para>
